  "time_ut": 1658835052,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd  \u0baa\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f  \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A life taken by hospital staff",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person who was seriously injured in a vehicle accident in Kandy-Akkuranai area died due to the refusal of hospital staff to admit him.",
        "The deceased has been identified as 58-year-old Mohammad Rilwan from Akkurana-Karamla area.",
        "The man, who runs a hotel in Akkurnai area, met with an accident when he went to a nearby shop to buy ginger to provide tea to those in fuel queues in Akkurnai town.",
        "After this, when his son brought his father to the Kandy National Hospital in a car, one of the staff there said that they do not take responsibility for patients on Thursdays and Sundays and refused to take responsibility for the accident victim.",
        "While the hospital staff did not even come forward to give first aid to the accident victim, they refused to provide an ambulance to transport the patient to the Peradana hospital.",
        "After this, when his son called the 1990 emergency ambulance service, they replied that they do not carry patients from one hospital to another.",
        "After this, with the help of an ambulance driver of the Kandy Hospital, after paying Rs 6,500, the accident victim was taken to the Peradana Hospital in a private ambulance, where he died.",
        "Peradanai Teaching Hospital Sudden Death Investigation Officer Amal Jayawardena said that the affected parties have appealed to the Ministry of Health regarding the non-responsibility of the patient at the Kandy National Hospital and the director of the Kandy National Hospital will take action in this regard."
      ],
